acked entity or one event). DuckDB generates\nthe full nested JSON structure including attributes, enrollments, events,\nand data values -- the Java code does zero JSON construction, just\nconcatenates pre-built strings into chunked payloads.\n\nThis enables arbitrarily large pre-generated datasets: ndjson.gz\ncompresses ~20x (4.4MB -\u003e 230KB for 1K patients), making 100K+ patient\nfiles practical to store in S3 or git LFS.\n\n- Add NdjsonFeeder: reads gzipped ndjson, chunks N lines per request\n- Remove CsvFeeder and all Java-side JSON/payload generation\n- SQL scripts now output ndjson instead of CSV\n- generate.sh pipes DuckDB output through gzip","author":{"name":"teleivo","email":"teleivo@users.noreply.github.com"},"id":"cf582ace7d28e9936d28d34c2c615c76c1429bac","tree_id":"d598b79197ec08fe1771fd3e72a5877f179bf01c","timestamp":"2026-03-17T12:02:13Z","committer":{"name":"teleivo","email":"teleivo@users.noreply.github.com"}},"workflow_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/workflows/10954","repository":{"id":66940520,"node_id":"MDEwOlJlcG9zaXRvcnk2Njk0MDUyMA==","owner":{"login":"dhis2","id":1089987,"node_id":"MDEyOk9yZ2FuaXphdGlvbjEwODk5ODc=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1089987?v=4","html_url":"https://github.com/dhis2","gravatar_id":"","type":"Organization","site_admin":false,"url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/events{/privacy}","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/following{/other_user}","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/followers","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/gists{/gist_id}","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/orgs","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/received_events","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/repos","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/subscriptions